div.div:
Lines represent Qt Signal - Slot connections
Boxes represent instantiated classes
Communication is ONLY via Qt Signal - Slot connections supported to guarantee thread safety
https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/threads-qobject.html#signals-and-slots-across-threads
Red Line: Blocking Queued
Green Line: Queued
Orange Line: Don't care
Red and Green Lines: Connected by the Controller class
Orange Line: Has to be connected by the user
Solid box: Own thread, handled by the Controller
Dashed box: Don't care, handled by the user
Green Box: Provided by the framework
Red box: Has to be implemented by the user
